''' Tilawa Viento Surf Center''' is a noted [[windsurfing]] centre, located on the northwestern shore of [[Lake Arenal]] in [[Guanacaste Province]] in northwest [[Costa Rica]]. The lake receives strong winds between November and March and is rated as one of the finest windsurfing locations in the world.<ref>{{cite book|author=Baker, C.P.|title=Costa Rica|publisher=[[Dorling Kindersley]] [[Eye Witness Travel Guides]]|year=2005|pages=152}}</ref> The centre, which opened in 1993, offers lessons to visitors of all standards.

